data.description: Don't miss all this home has to offer.  Nice residential area with a lot of new construction on Blackstone Road and in the Development.  No HOA , 13 miles from RSW International Airport, minutes from shopping, movie theaters and schools but feels like country living.  Here is your chance to own this Mirror Lakes heated pool home. Split bedroom floor plan 3 bedrooms 2 bath 2 car garage (with new garage opener with 2 remotes, and ceiling fan). Home with separate dining room area and breakfast bar.  Beautiful kitchen with stainless steel appliances.  Laundry room with washer and dryer, brand new tankless water heater, brand new pool pump and new pool heather, pool cage screen was just replace. Master bath features dual sinks with separate shower and large soaking tub.  Guest bathroom has a door leading into the pool area. A/C replaced in 2016. Gutters all around the home, and will have a brand new roof before closing. By appointment only.
